	<h3>Vinyl Fence Age Analysis</h3>
	<p>Vinyl fences behave differently - condition less age-dependent:</p>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>0-10 years:</strong> Should require minimal repairs - manufacturer defects only</li>
		<li><strong>10-20 years:</strong> Repairs economical - material doesn't deteriorate like wood</li>
		<li><strong>20-25 years:</strong> Assess UV damage and brittleness, often still repairable</li>
		<li><strong>25+ years:</strong> Replacement parts may be unavailable for older styles</li>
		<li><strong>Key factor:</strong> Impact damage main concern, not age-related decay</li>
	</ul>

