		<li><strong>0-10 years:</strong> Repair almost always best choice</li>
		<li><strong>10-15 years:</strong> Check for widespread rust - localized repair OK</li>
		<li><strong>15+ years:</strong> If rust widespread, replacement more economical</li>
	</ul>

